(173, 34, 36, 'Citan', 8, 'SWTOR Obroan PvP armor and weapon preview', 'A gallery of the Obroan PvP armor and weapons models added to the SWTOR PTS as of the latest update. Players can expect these PvP armor in Patch 2.4. Obroan are brought with Conqueror armor pieces and ranked warzone commendations.\r\n\r\nNote: PTS notes says these models are still placeholders but it is likely a copy/paste error. That being said, these could non-final and still subjected to change\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nhttp://dulfy.net/2013/08/30/swtor-obroan-pvp-armor-and-weapon-preview/\r\n\r\n\r\nMfg', '2013-09-12 13:46:47'),
(174, 34, 36, 'Citan', 8, 'SWTOR Obroan PvE armor and weapon preview', 'SWTOR Possible models for the Dread Forged new PvE armor\r\n\r\nPatch 2.4, SWTOR\r\n\r\nby dulfy	\r\n\r\nSWTOR Dread Forged armor set, a new PvE set to be introduced in patch 2.4, has being added to the PTS. While the armors are still using placeholders, the vendors are possibly wearing some of it. Here are some screenshots to pique your interest. Update: Weapons have also being added. \r\n\r\nThe new armor set is rating 180 with 78 mods. This is better than the Kell Dragon gear gained from Nightmare TFB and S&V. Set bonus remains the same. \r\n\r\nhttp://dulfy.net/2013/08/29/swtor-possible-models-for-the-dread-forged-new-pve-armor/', '2013-09-12 13:46:47'),
